{"tid":1525920,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"經過琴晚，愛港鐵愛香港，港鐵係今次運動關鍵","createTime":"2019-09-01T03:34:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T12:58:18.000Z","uid":297169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"894b1c893056f9a1410cc04655020d94fcb2dc77","tid":1525920,"uid":297169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:34:30.000Z","msg":"港鐵係係全世界最便捷交通工具，呢一點大家都認同，港人每日返工放工都依懶佢，今次<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">返送中運動都唔例外</span></span><br />\n<br />\n運動要暢順要有流動性，成日講<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Be water</span></span>都係咁解，所以搞地鐵做咩，我地要愛佢保護佢，你破壞地鐵運作，作有藉口唔開，理義士點走，唔都封晒，用跑嫁！而且地鐵有好多市民，大部分同一陣線，佢地會保護你。<br />\n<br />\n今次<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不完美但可改善可接受</span></span>，混亂當中黑警無差別打市民，同元朗721事件無分別，雖然豬隊友，但冇佢地唔會暴露更多黑警惡行，冇差別打，打完唔拉，因為有鏡頭，打完快閃⋯嬲到震<br />\n<br />\n每次有錯誤我地都去討論去改，我們先可以行到今日，唔講咁多，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">[url]<span style=\"color: red;\">愛港鐵，力保港鐵暢順</span>[/url]</span>，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日機場見</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"a320f8223c441e9b62fcf5e7325c5c76b9ee7064","tid":1525920,"uid":297169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:35:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7a4bd6cda9f01971c70bb04b52a30a68aa3e7fc5","tid":1525920,"uid":297169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:35:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7129228f5587bcf9bab19bc46951a2dd2e8c05eb","tid":1525920,"uid":297169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:36:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fc49e8db6acdbd4d99b954b0114fde576eefbfb4","tid":1525920,"uid":297169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:37:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5c820ccd325516751da1d26b769648c877466f49","tid":1525920,"uid":297169,"like":0,"d